      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tatschu wiꞥſch no Uydens\nGmarschas attak iſplaukt/ un\naug tahdá Auguma ka Eedehsts."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet weens Wihr̄ no-\nmirſt/ kad tas wahisch tohp/ un\nkad Zilweks to Dwehſeli iſlaiſch/\nkur wiꞥſch tad paleek?"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee Uydeni iſtekk no Juh-\nxas/ un weena Uppe iſſikſt un\niſschuhſt."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta patt nogullahs Zil-\nweks un ne zelkahs attak/teeſams\ntahs Debbeſis wairs ne buhs/\ntee ne uſmohdifees/ un ne taps\nno fawa Meega uſmohdinati."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ak! kaut tu manni eekſch\nBedres apſlehptu/un (tur) man-\nni noſlehptu/ kamehr tawa Dut-\nmiba nowebrſtohs/(Kaut)tu man\nweenu Mehrki liktu/ un mannis\npeeminnetu."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad kahds Wihr̄ no-\nmirſt/ woj tas attak atdsibfees?\nes gaidifchu wiſa mannas Zih-\nnifchanas Laika/ kamehr manna\nPawebrtifchana ateet."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu faukti/ un es tew at-\nbildeſchu/ taws Rohku Darbs\ntervim eegrıbbetees."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet nu ſeaiti tu mannis\nSohtus/ un ne* apturreſti man-\nni mannu Grebku deht.\n* Ijabs dohd Leezibu fawas Tizzibas, ka\nDeews winnu Kappá ne apturrehs, bet liks at-\nkat augſchamzeltees."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Manna Pahrkahpschana\nirr weená Muskuli apſehgeleta/\nun tu fafeen mannu Noseegumu\nar weenn Pawehdeni."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Teescham/ weens Kalns\nfagruhſt/ kad tas friht/ un weens"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Akmina-Kalus tohp no\nWeetas niſzelts."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Uydens iſdoh\nmiuns/ un tee Semmes P\nli pahrpluhſt pahr faweem\nteem/ un ta Ztliveka Zerr\nleez ſuſt."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Woj tu winnu muh\nſpaidiſi/ kamehr wiſch a\nun pawehrtiſi winna Gihm\nmebr tu winnu palaidiſi?"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Teek winna Behrni\ndá/ tad to wiſch ne finna/\ntee beß Gohda/ ir to win\nteem ne famanna."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kamehr winnam ta\nfa irr/ tad irr Sahpes pahr\nnn/ un winna Dwehſelei\nwinna jaschehlojahs."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XV. Nodalla.\nEeliwas aprahi Jiabu/ ka wiſch tik le\nbesdeewign Wallodu runna : 1. U\nſiſt/ ka wiſch netaiſs irr : 4. Kur\npreekſch Deewa ne weens Zilweks :\nne weens Engelis taiſns efju : 15.\npehdigi/ ka Deews tikcai tohs Bebd\nun Blehdneekus tà mehds pahrmahj"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad atbildeja Ee-\ntas Teemaniteris/\nſazzija :\n2. Buhs tad weenam\nram Wihr̄am weltigu Si\nſchannu iſrunnaht? un tawu ?\nderu ar Wehju pildiht?\n3. Pahrmahzidams ar W\ndeem/ kas ne peeklahjabs / u\nWallodu / kam ne tahds\nbums atlezz.\n4. Teetcham/ tu atmettin\n(Deewa) Bibjaschann/ un"
    }
  ],
